{"tid":898143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲大陸仔往雞雞塞14顆磁球　一跑步就會痛","createTime":"2018-11-11T12:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T14:16:13.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba0df0ec657b689407fe61f7d70b65a66c3af98","tid":898143,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"中國一名13歲少年，把磁球往自己尿道內塞，結果磁球進入他的身體內取不出，直到一年半後身體不舒服，告訴父母後才就醫將磁求取出。<br />\n<br />\n據《南方都市報》報導，中國深圳13歲少年小浩（化名），前年一人在家無聊，就把磁球塞進雞雞，進入尿道後取不出，起初他還有些擔心，但因身體沒有不舒服，也就沒放在心上，只有跑步時感覺到小磁球的存在。過了一年半後，小浩開始感覺身體不舒服，跑步、小便都會痛，告訴父母後才上醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n醫生拍X光片後發現，這些磁珠緊緊連在一起，固定在膀胱左側壁。手術當天，透過膀胱鏡能看到，這些磁球已經生鏽黏在膀胱左側，但因磁力影響，鉗子一進去就會被磁球吸住，鉗子也很難鉗死小磁球，於是醫生利用磁球的吸力，將全部磁球引入到穿刺器，在拔出穿刺器的同時，成功帶出了所有的磁球。<br />\n<br />\n醫生指出，從小浩體內取出整整14顆磁球，每個直徑0.5公分。小浩當晚尿液就變清，第二天就能正常吃飯活動，很快就康復出院。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"4a60bfc9c7470e3a0891b02a0349dd8e975885f8","tid":898143,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8974c813da958a4d901f8ec32a97fed2ac700d35","tid":898143,"uid":220701,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戇鳩冇藥醫"},{"pid":"d5522dd78e1c6f969aad30e29d9803b867e236fa","tid":898143,"uid":182930,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"繼自己割包皮後又有新力作<br />\n自己入珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c7e8b572a5ffb64357f529741de50dc0a741f6","tid":898143,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c884dcbe345c3897ec48d54738f91cb24bd9a165","tid":898143,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"一年半後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8923d3e26e999074d1add444f7b7cdbe175c5598","tid":898143,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"0.5公分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全長7cm，到底一開始點塞落去"},{"pid":"0a83dc7383c2038348ec1edd434fb8d186931738","tid":898143,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"點解會生秀"}]}